<p><a href="http://fastenyourseatbelts.at/images/2011/07/facebookseiten.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1548" title="facebookseiten" src="http://fastenyourseatbelts.at/images/2011/07/facebookseiten-300x258.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="258" /></a></p>
